    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and full of potential, this vehicle is a practical choice for a buyer who wants dependable basic transportation at an accessible price. It shows its age and is best suited for someone comfortable with a well-used vehicle, but it still offers solid value as an economical daily driver, starter car, or backup vehicle. A straightforward, affordable opportunity for the right owner.",
      "price": 5995.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car you can put straight to work or tidy up over time? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s an honest old motor with plenty of life left for the right buyer. A great option for someone who wants cheap wheels, a handy runaround, or a project to make their own. Priced fairly for what it is, and represented with no nonsense \u2014 if you want something budget-friendly and approachable, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Strong-running used car with solid bones and plenty of potential. The powertrain pulls well, shifts through the gears as it should, and the chassis feels like a great candidate for someone wanting dependable transportation or a straightforward project. It shows cosmetic wear and needs attention in a few areas, but the fundamentals are there: usable, complete, and ready for an owner who appreciates a mechanically promising platform. A lot of car for the money.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way to get on the road fast. Rough around the edges, priced to move. First serious buyer takes it.",
      "price": 7900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "A true diamond-in-the-rough with unmistakable personality, this car has the kind of honest, road-worn character that turns heads and sparks ideas. Its presence feels vintage, gritty, and full of possibility\u2014the perfect canvas for a hands-on owner, weekend tinkerer, or anyone looking for an affordable ride with soul. There\u2019s a lot of story here, and for the right buyer, even more still to be written.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Budget-friendly and priced to move, this vehicle offers straightforward value for anyone seeking affordable transportation without unnecessary frills. It presents as a practical opportunity for a commuter, first-time buyer, or project-minded owner looking for solid utility at an accessible price. A smart way to get on the road for less.",
      "price": 5995.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable set of wheels with plenty of life left for the right person? This car isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a genuine budget-friendly option for someone who needs basic transport, a first project, or a handy runaround. It has the usual signs of age and wear you\u2019d expect, but it still offers solid value at this price point. If you\u2019re practical, don\u2019t mind a few cosmetic and mechanical odds and ends, and want something cheap to get into, this could be a great fit. Priced to sell and worth a look.",
      "price": 4950.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project car with good bones and a drivetrain that still shows promise. Starts, runs, and offers a strong foundation for someone who appreciates mechanical simplicity and is looking for an affordable platform to sort, restore, or build. Body and cosmetic condition reflect age and use, but the chassis feels like it has more to give. Great candidate for a budget daily fixer, weekend wrenching project, or parts-savvy enthusiast build. Priced to move for someone who knows what they\u2019re looking at.",
      "price": 6850.0,
